'''Albania–Ukraine relations''' are [[foreign relations]] between [[Albania]] and [[Ukraine]].  The diplomatic relations between Albania and Ukraine were established in 1922. 
Both countries have a non resident ambassador based in [[Warsaw]], Poland. Albania also has an honorary consul in [[Kharkiv]].<ref>http://usa.mfa.gov.ua/en/about-ukraine/dip-in-ukraine/missions-list/2</ref>

