==Relations with Central Asia== The Committee on Foreign Affairs has established strong cooperation with Kazakhstan, Central Asia's most prosperous country, through regular visits and meetings. The European Parliament and Kazakhstan hold annual meetings of Parliamentary Cooperation Committee.<ref>{{cite web |title=Kazakhstan - EU cooperation |url=http://mfa.gov.kz/en/content-view/sotrudnichestvo-s-evropejskim-soyuzom |website=mfa.gov.kz}}</ref>
