'''Financial Bank Benin''' is a [[commercial bank]] in [[Benin]]. It is a member of the [[West African Bankers' Association]].

It has its headquarters in [[Cotonou]] but also has branches in cities such as [[Parakou]]. The bank is dominated by [[Switzerland|Swiss]] ownership, with Financial BC in Geneva having an 85% share, Aiglon S.A. in Geneva with 15%  and private French shares (0.01%).<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wabao.biz/home/waba/bank_benin.html|title=List of banks in Benin|publisher=West African Bankers' Association |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090227134311/http://www.wabao.biz/home/waba/bank_benin.html |archive-date=27 February 2009 |accessdate=11 January 2009}}</ref>

The bank has a 25% share in the Benin [[microfinance]] group [[Finadev]].

